parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the CVT transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, jerk, or hesitate while driving, leading to loss of control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or jerks when accelerating
stalls while driving
has difficulty shifting gears
and may produce unusual noises or vibrations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transfer case can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, leading to accidents or strandings.
symptoms: The vehicle leaks fluid
has difficulty shifting gears
and may produce unusual noises or vibrations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine and transmission performance can cause the vehicle to hesitate or jerk while driving, leading to loss of control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or jerks when accelerating
stalls while driving
and may produce unusual noises or vibrations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the OCS can cause the passenger airbag to malfunction, leading to potential injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The passenger airbag off indicator light stays on even when an adult passenger is in the seat
the airbag fails to deploy in an accident
the airbag deploys but does not inflate
and the system intermittently malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in an accident can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag fails to deploy in an accident
the airbag deploys but does not inflate
and the passenger airbag off indicator light stays on even when an adult passenger is in the seat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical issues can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to potential injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag system malfunctions
the passenger airbag off indicator light stays on even when an adult passenger is in the seat
and the vehicle's electrical system experiences glitches.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden explosion of the sunroof can cause injury to occupants, distraction, and loss of control, leading to accidents.
symptoms: Loud explosion sound
shattered glass
and sudden loss of sunroof functionality.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning AEB system can cause the vehicle to stop suddenly, leading to accidents or injuries, or fail to stop in emergency situations, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: False collision warnings
sudden stopping of the vehicle
and failure of the AEB system to function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and transmission can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Sluggish acceleration
shuddering
and hesitation when shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unreliable door locks can cause inconvenience, delay, and potentially lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Failure of door locks to lock or unlock
and unreliable door lock functionality.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning backup camera and sensors can cause accidents or injuries, especially when reversing.
symptoms: Failure of the backup camera to display images
failure of sensors to detect obstacles
and false warnings.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning ABS actuator can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Failure of the ABS actuator to function properly
and failure of the ABS light to illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning navigation system can cause distraction, delay, and potentially lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: GPS routing errors
misrouting
and failure of the navigation system to provide accurate directions.
